{"tid":1008624,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港特首林鄭以粵語向港人拜年","createTime":"2019-02-04T15:39:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-04T16:51:51.000Z","uid":56984,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ce14f08fef86875139c1b60b75812e89a233a7ed","tid":1008624,"uid":56984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T15:39:30.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥發表農曆新年賀辭，她說，新一年是豬年，祝願市民來年事事如意、身體健康、家庭幸福。<br />\n      <br />\n      賀辭全片長約1分鐘，林鄭月娥穿上紅色中式服裝，到上環選購海味和年花，更不時與多名市民影相及握手，又向市民拜年。<br />\n      <br />\n      林鄭月娥表示，「農曆新年是中國人特別重視的節日，也是一家人珍惜相聚的時刻，許多市民在過年前都會四出辦年貨，市面洋溢一片熱鬧氣氛。我也忙裏偷閒，到上環買海味食材和年花，跟店鋪東主和員工閒話家常，亦趁機會和市民提早拜年，互相送上節日祝福。」<br />\n      <br />\n      與去不同，林鄭月娥丈夫林兆波今年未有在新年賀辭片段中出現向市民拜年。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.stheadline.com/inews-content.php?cat=a&amp;nid=24997\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.stheadline.com%2Finews-content.php%3Fcat%3Da%26nid%3D24997&d=KChxWXaIVet3ZRtCu1MdJ%2FYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=283343bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.stheadline.com%2Finews-content.php%3Fcat%3Da%26nid%3D24997&h=f1819d3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.stheadline.com/inews-content.php?cat=a&amp;nid=24997</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好親民喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b05b64697a23d2cd21018f7d135a5ab1ff6654f","tid":1008624,"uid":56984,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T15:40:30.000Z","msg":"唔知連登仔like唔like<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\"